{"tid":1653795,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[iOS 12/13] Safari會send你IP畀中國騰訊(如果你enable咗「詐騙網站警告」)","createTime":"2019-10-14T08:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T04:45:34.000Z","uid":287893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b88692cc3fff36b63313550617e7bbcc4cc93b88","tid":1653795,"uid":287893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:59:05.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/ios13-safari-sends-safe-browsing-data-to-tencent\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fios13-safari-sends-safe-browsing-data-to-tencent&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAhw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=cd4a6044\" target=\"_blank\">https://mrmad.com.tw/ios13-safari-sends-safe-browsing-data-to-tencent</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄自原文<br />\n<br />\n「... 在 Safari 這項「詐騙網站警告」功能只要啟用後，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最初蘋果設計只會將資料傳送到 Google 安全瀏覽服務來實現檢查是否安全，不過再升級至 iOS 13 後，多出了中國「騰訊安全瀏覽」和原有「Google 安全瀏覽」能用來檢查詐騙網站，導致使用者只要使用 Safari 安全瀏覽服務後，就會讓使用者 IP 位置傳送到 Google 和騰訊記錄。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n過去約翰&middot;霍普金斯大學的 Matthew Green也曾分析過，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">理論上只要有企圖的公司將Google 安全瀏覽數據和網頁要求配對，就能輕易辨識身份，當然在中國的騰訊也同樣是有能力可以收集到這些 IP 位置，並且變成大數據並且進一步分析。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">會採用騰訊安全瀏覽服務，蘋果最初是針對中國大陸地區的 Safari ，用來取代當地無法連 Google 問題，不過目前已經將騰訊整合到全世界 iOS 13 版本上，導致每個鄰近地區用戶都可能造成 IP 被中國騰訊記錄。</span></span>...」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>阻擋 iOS 12、iOS 13 Safari 會偷傳送用戶IP 給騰訊教學</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>進入「設定」&gt;「Safari」內將「詐騙網站警告」功能關閉即可。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"359597f6ff5275b48ae55a2c8c723ea9f731a4d5","tid":1653795,"uid":287893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:00:20.000Z","msg":"節錄自原文<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">更新：檢查後連 iOS 12 Safari 也同樣中獎，iOS 12 用戶也記得關閉。</span></span>」"},{"pid":"0a16040f7472137119803c07409cd373c141c747","tid":1653795,"uid":287893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:01:37.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到，搵人散出去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1b7a2d69bebc220854973d9c0e0594e8381037","tid":1653795,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:07:20.000Z","msg":"10.14 人權民主法集氣大會🇺🇸<br />\n時間：晚上七點正<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園"},{"pid":"da362e12b90c54e8e5694df3bc41c143125756e1","tid":1653795,"uid":155781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:34:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cb86d2669787228b6d135a5c3a78a36bb3f0caf","tid":1653795,"uid":75009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T10:51:42.000Z","msg":"幫"},{"pid":"7952e9cc1c9d25da6278e456426faa7b8e6641aa","tid":1653795,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T13:19:36.000Z","msg":"初部話係真。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KIknIquYjw8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKIknIquYjw8&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAhw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=e6c9609e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KIknIquYjw8</a>"},{"pid":"750e8d72c29cb439da018d11527c83b6351e1d7e","tid":1653795,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T16:15:53.000Z","msg":"你肯定關閉功能可以停止傳送資料去Google/騰訊？<br />\n而唔係純粹關閉警告功能？"},{"pid":"bcc79803c4a9b020ba4d3eebc00acf7d635056f5","tid":1653795,"uid":327266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:53:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/10/14/20913680/apple-tencent-privacy-controversy-safe-browsing-blacklist-explainer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2